    "created_at": "2015-10-29T17:01:53Z",
    "updated_at": "2015-10-29T17:01:53Z",
    "body": "> This is a privacy issue, since any website you visit in a webview can access your precise location. If something like a web browser is created using electron, any website visited using it could access your location.\n\nElectron isn't designed to be a web browser, Electron is a platform for writing Desktop applications, and Desktop applications can access location data\n"
