    "created_at": "2015-10-30T01:12:05Z",
    "updated_at": "2015-10-30T01:12:05Z",
    "body": "> Desktop applications can access location data\n\nI agree. The issue isn't that an app can access location data, the issue is that content inside a webview, which according to the docs is for untrusted content, can access location data even though the docs say that content inside it \"doesn't have the same permissions as your web page\".\n"
