    "body": "Having this would be cool, but I don't think any of us would be interested in this since only few people care running untrusted content securely, and you can always use `preload` script to add a custom wrapper around the geolocation API, so I'm closing this issue.\n\nHowever pull request to implement this is still welcomed.\n"
